-- Coles shares put on trading halt
-- 
-- Mon Apr 2, 2007 8:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/04/03/us-coles-wesfarmers-halt-idUSSYU00209820070403

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Shares in Australian retailer Coles Group Ltd. CGJ.AX were placed on a trading halt on Tuesday pending the release of an announcement from the company. 

 Earlier, Wesfarmers WES.AX said it had acquired an 11.3 percent voting stake in Coles and was pursuing discussions with the group. ($1=A$1.22)